        <mxCell id="pipeline-simulation" value="&lt;b&gt;Pipeline Simulation&lt;/b&gt;&#xa;&#xa;• Input dataset profile before actual run&#xa;• View XGBoost predictions&#xa;  (bottleneck/duration/resource)&#xa;&#xa;OUT: REST POST /api/simulate" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#2a1a3a;strokeColor=#8844cc;fontColor=#ddbbff;fontSize=10;verticalAlign=top;arcSize=8;align=left;spacingLeft=6;" vertex="1" parent="1">
